waking up to an odd dream i had an odd dream the other night and i think my dream is telling me something about my feelings i had a dream that i was at work and my manager gave me a paper on the paper was a list of all my friends and my ex and my ex's poem i read it and started crying one of my co workers sat down next to me and gave me a hug it felt so real in my dream that i was really hurt i woke up and i was actually crying i thought it was the strangest experience of a dream is there meaning behind this dream in some way i believe it maybe that i've been hiding some of my feelings of my ex we broke up on good terms but we don't really talk much anymore we have both are so busy w our lives that we barely talk anymore i honestly still miss this person but i realized that we both need to move on i thought i had but this dream seems to tell me otherwise i use to read and study about dreams but i really don't know much about this in my case what does this experience mean according to dreamcrowd to see your friends in your dream signifies aspects of your personality that you have rejected but are ready to integrate these rejected part of yourself the relationships you have with those around you are important in learning about yourself additionally this symbol foretells of happy tidings from them and the arrival of good news to see your childhood friend in your dream signifies regression into your past where you had no responsibilities and things were much simpler and carefree you may be wanting to escape the the pressures and stresses of adulthood consider the relationship you had with this friend and the lessons that were learned alternatively the childhood friend may be suggesting that you have been acting in a childish manner and you need to start acting like an adult to dream that your best friend is dying suggests that some aspect or quality that your best friend possess is dying within your own self to see a lover in your dream symbolizes acceptance self worth 